 months after the closure of the account. This is for ensure that we still have the ability to help with any complaints, insurance cases, or criminal investigations related to a previous reservation. If you want to remove specific information shared with another user before the deletion period ends, contact us by email with a request in which specify what information you want to remove. We will remove the information as soon as possible, and in any case not more than 30 days after receipt of a valid application by written. We reserve the right to refuse removal if the removal request is related to a claim active or potential customer, insurance case, or criminal investigation. Contact details are in the section 7 ("Contact").',
